=\"font-size:12px\">【专业履历】</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"> 1995.02-1998.04&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> <span style=\"font-size:12px\">清华大学</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"> 1995.08-1999.10&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> <span style=\"font-size:12px\">清华大学建筑与城市研究所副所长</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">1998.05-</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">至今<span>&nbsp; </span>清华大学</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">1992.08-</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">至今 &nbsp;清华大学建筑学院、清华大学城市规划设计研究院执教并从事科研、生产工作</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2000.04-</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">至今<span>&nbsp; </span>清华大学博士生导师</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">1999.10-</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">至今<span>&nbsp; </span>北京清华同衡规划设计研究院有限公司（原北京清华城市规划设计研究院）董事长兼院长</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2013.03-</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">至今<span>&nbsp; </span>清控人居建设（集团）有限公司董事长兼总经理</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><s